{"tid":926200,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"我朋友短髮控因為一套動畫，而幫佢對抗到癌症。","createTime":"2018-12-03T09:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T15:05:32.000Z","uid":8307,"like":58,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"ef9d0e0800f25eeff7af111c5ba909ab05b75be2","tid":926200,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:26:21.000Z","msg":"我同連登會然短髮控由細識到大<br />\n細細個佢已經食雞唔食雞皮，食橙就食埋橙皮<br />\n開頭以為佢有少少弱智，叫過佢去睇醫生啦醫生話佢冇野<br />\n大個少少有次病發先法國佢患上左視網膜母細胞瘤，<br />\n其中一隻眼已經好嚴重，要剝左佢<br />\n剝密之後<br />\n初頭佢好唔開心成日發脾氣，<br />\n自從東京食屎仔播左之後，因為佢好鐘意套野<br />\n佢就覺得戴眼罩可以扮金木研幾有型睇開左<br />\n<br />\n早排佢個病又復發，<br />\n佢好驚要剝埋第二隻眼，就話<br />\n如果有刀劍神域咁既遊戲，我冇眼都可以玩到 幾好<br />\n<br />\n我由消息人士得知刀劍神域會出新動畫<br />\n同佢講：你盲左就冇得睇<br />\n佢終於用意志力同療程對抗到癌魔康復返<br />\n<br />\n所以佢先咁鐘情於刀劍神域<br />\n唔好再反佢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8ee789890c375e161f7821563ee62045836284","tid":926200,"uid":2794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:27:07.000Z","msg":"👌🏻"},{"pid":"6858de2621c663af2b043139bfea3814f9027d13","tid":926200,"uid":2090,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:27:45.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 0分"},{"pid":"c4a783a628b4ed7da3f7e02830fbbe0b7739cdb5","tid":926200,"uid":146340,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"佢第三隻眼都畀人屌到用唔到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b848c161d2ee4196c6e0d10ac7feb5f1b707afc6","tid":926200,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T09:28:50.000Z","msg":"原來背後有一個咁嘅故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31e2088119382414117dad995b32b8c3ce6c53f","tid":926200,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20